    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this car\u2014it's an absolute gem! It\u2019s in total mint condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, so it's spotless inside and out and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
