      "description": "This is a true museum-quality specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory fragrance; the premium leather seats show no signs of entry wear or bolster compression, and every electronic component functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service record with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule using only OEM parts. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched trunk tools, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth.",
